data.description: Detached single family home in Deanwood!  2 Bedrooms and 1 full bath home on large lot.  Corner lot  located on 49th Pl and Hayes wide streets, street parking and ability to create off street parking.  Main level has screened front porch entrance.  Walk into main level hallway living room on left with dining room.  Galley kitchen off the dining room with rear exit.  Second level has 2 good sized bedrooms and full bath.  Basement is unfinished with walkout and windows.  House needs work. Good bones.   Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity to make this property your own!  Being sold AS-IS .  Cash or conventional. 3rd party approval needed.
